    <description>THE ONLY PLUGIN YOU NEED!!!!!!!

Get those LLMs to do your NetBeans work.

This plugin is an extension Anahata's "pure java" gemini client (gemini-java-client) with extra 
@AITools specially crafted so the LLM can actually operate netbeans.

- Gives the LLM an instant overview of yuor IDE on every round including:
  - directory / source code package structures, 
  - file and folder sizes 
  - last modified timestamps
  - any IDE alerts (compilation errors, warnings, etc)

- Git integration (can open a commit dialog for you)

- Take screenshots of your IDE so the LLM can understand visually what you are saying (specially useful for debugging UI)

- Automatic context window management (tell the model what context window size you want to work with)

- Model choosing (just gemini models supported atm)

- Save chat sessions, load previous chat sessions

- The LLM can write, compile and run java code at runtime inside the NetBeans JVM
</description>
